00:38:17,505 --> 00:38:21,265
Otherwise, you wouldn't come help me
and make things turn out like this.

271
00:38:21,345 --> 00:38:22,465
Right?

272
00:38:24,825 --> 00:38:27,225
But I don't think I helped anyone.

273
00:38:29,225 --> 00:38:32,105
But you helped me a lot.

274
00:38:34,985 --> 00:38:38,825
Actually, I gained a lot from you too.

275
00:38:42,265 --> 00:38:44,105
Do you want anything else from me?

276
00:39:00,825 --> 00:39:01,905
That's it?

277
00:39:05,505 --> 00:39:06,985
<i>Would it be okay</i>

278
00:39:07,945 --> 00:39:09,945
<i>if I asked to stay by your side forever?</i>

279
00:39:19,585 --> 00:39:21,625
<i>You won't be able to find me, Sky.</i>

280
00:39:48,465 --> 00:39:49,505
They've been upskirting us.

281
00:39:49,585 --> 00:39:51,305
You have to deal with them, Teacher.

282
00:39:55,025 --> 00:39:57,385
I'm Nanno. I'm a new student here.

283
00:39:57,465 --> 00:39:59,065
Why did you want to study here?

284
00:39:59,145 --> 00:40:00,545
The guys here are cute.

285
00:40:01,145 --> 00:40:02,665
And they're nice too.

286
00:40:03,265 --> 00:40:04,105
Nanno.

287
00:40:04,185 --> 00:40:06,465
I bet she could go for a high price.

288
00:40:07,065 --> 00:40:08,425
You don't have to secretly film me.

289
00:40:09,025 --> 00:40:11,945
<i>If you just ask nicely,</i>
<i>I'd show you anyway.</i>

290
00:40:14,105 --> 00:40:15,465
Take it.

291
00:42:08,945 --> 00:42:11,945
